reviewText: This movie has the worst sets and corny, corny lines.  This cast must be starting acting school because it is that bad.  My 3 and 4 year old Grand Children laughed at how bad it was.  They couldn't get through it and I had to agree.  This had to have been some write-off excuse for someone?  I do NOT recommend.
This movie isn't available in a US DVD format, so I bought this one and had it converted. My daughter LOVES it!
